      "effect": "Each player can Special Summon 1 DARK Spellcaster monster from their hand or Deck (but neither player can activate their effects this turn), then if you Special Summoned a monster whose original name is \"Dark Magician\" or \"Dark Magician Girl\", you can add 1 Spell/Trap that mentions \"Dark Magician\" from your Deck to your hand, except \"Dark Magical Curtain\". You can only activate 1 \"Dark Magical Curtain\" per turn.",
      "official": false
    },
